    <div class="blueBox"> 
     <div> 
      <!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="Right Callout" --> 
      <h2 class="h1StyleTitles">Fast Facts</h2> 
      <p class="fastfacts">Expenditures of the Oklahoma public higher education system generate <span class="subnavColorBoldRed">$9.2 billion</span> in economic output impacts in the state and support more than <span class="subnavColorBoldRed">85,000</span> Oklahoma jobs.</p> 
      <p class="fastfacts">The estimated return on investment for Oklahoma public higher education is <span class="subnavColorBoldRed">$4.72 </span>for every $1 of state funding.</p> 
      <p><span class="fastfacts">Enrollment at near-record levels continues, with more than </span><span class="subnavColorBoldRed">186,000</span> <span class="fastfacts">students enrolled for academic year 2013</span>.</p> 
      <p><span class="fastfacts">The U.S. Chamber of Commerce ranks Oklahoma higher education </span><span class="subnavColorBoldRed">No. 5 in the nation in affordability</span>.</p> 
